    <item>
      <title>Libby - Page 1</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/libby/page1/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/libby/page1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;page-1&#34;&gt;Page 1&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the first private page in the Libby section.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;content&#34;&gt;Content&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can put any content here that you want to share with specific people via direct links.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Private&lt;/strong&gt;: Not listed in navigation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accessible&lt;/strong&gt;: Via direct URL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Secure&lt;/strong&gt;: Only people with the link can find it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-content&#34;&gt;Example Content&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
